Our product is an AI-powered multifunctional image creation platform that combines Text-to-Image, Image-to-Image, and Inpainting capabilities, deeply integrated with Photoshop-level editing tools, enabling unrestricted creativity.

Key Features
● Integration with webui
● Open and edit PSD, XCP, Sketch (Photoshop, GIMP, and Sketch), or any other image files
● Text-to-Image: Quickly generate creative images by entering simple text descriptions, meeting the needs of illustration, concept design, and more.
● Image-to-Image: Upload images and adjust them with text, generating enhanced designs based on the original image, such as style transfer and detail enhancement.
● Inpainting: Leverage AI technology to repair image defects or replace specific areas, seamlessly integrating new content.
● Advanced Editing: Integrates Photoshop-level functionality for fine-tuning and creative design of generated images.

Use Cases
● Personal Creation: Whether for artistic creation or fun design, quickly bring your ideas to life.
● Commercial Design: Provide efficient image solutions for advertising, branding, and product design.
● Education & Research: Support the digital development of art education and creative research.

Product Highlights
● AI-powered with fast generation speed and realistic results.
● Flexible creation with multi-mode interaction and deep customization.
● No professional skills required—anyone can become a creative expert.
Unlock your creative potential with AI—turn your ideas into reality in just one step!
